title: Hour 3 - Michael Wilbon (06-09-20)

description:
Michael Wilbon tells Dan that Northwestern was definitly not a party school. Michael is discouraged by the two sides negotiating for major league baseball. Michael says they have blown up an MLB season before and it looks like it may happen again.
